      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "The Delegation of Cangrejos performed the following set list in 2026 for Encuentro de Tambores: "
            },
            {
              "bold": true,
              "text": "“Cunya de la Peromia,” “Misereriere,” \"Plere Maria\", “Petronila Guilbe,” “Ay, mis Barriles,”"
            },
            {
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "bold": true,
              "text": "“La Borucana”"
            },
            {
              "text": " in the Plaza de los Obreros on March 29. The festival began at 1:00 p.m. and concluded at 5:00 p.m. Delegations arrived as early as 6:00 a.m. for registration. I was part of this year’s delegation, which was directed by Caridad Martínez, daughter of Tata Cepeda, and dedicated to Tite Curet Alonso, the renowned salsero honored this year."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "\n\n"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
